   (4) A = log10( 2 ) 
-> (5) A = 0.30103

   (6) B = log10(2*t)
-> (7) B = 0.30103 + log10(t)

   (8) C = log10(0.5+2*t)
-> (9) C = log10(0.5+2*t)

