   (11) % Example 2: log10   (complex scalar expressions)
   (12) %--------------------------------------------------------------------
   (13) D = log10( 2 + 3*GetImaginaryNumber() )
-> (14) D = 0.5569717 + 0.4268219*imaginary

   (15) E = log10( 3*GetImaginaryNumber() + t )
-> (16) E = log10(3*imaginary+t)

